summary: I was telling a friend of mine (born 1982) that she’s exactly between Sandra Oh (’71) and Jodie Comer (’93) in age, and she got...
body:
I was telling a friend of mine (born 1982) that she’s exactly between Sandra Oh (’71) and Jodie Comer (’93) in age, and she got really quiet, and I said, “Sorry, did I make you feel old?”

And she said, “No, I was just thinking about being exactly between Sandra Oh and Jodie Comer in… more literal ways.”

summary: Do you think a producer leaked the picture? its strange that they didnt post it on the instagram account. Makes me think it was...
question: Do you think a producer leaked the picture? its strange that they didnt post it on the instagram account. Makes me think it was a mistake and we were not supposed to see it... so then maybe thats as steamy as its going to get and nothing else :(
answer:
@villanellesstrap @innatelymagical @killingvillaneve @curlyeve and i decided that it was probably a purposeful leak because it was on a press site. honestly, i don’t think they’d let such a spoiler-y picture get out without it being intentional. 

it was most likely released to hype everyone up for the episode and create more buzz. producers and social media teams are calculating and precise. 

if it was an accident, someone’s dumb ass definitely got fired, though.
